===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# The action or process of [[graduate|graduating]] and receiving a diploma for completing a course of study (such as from an [[educational institution]]).
# A [[commencement]] ceremony.
# {{sciences}} A marking (i.e. on a container) indicating a measurement.
# The exposure of a liquid in large surfaces to the air, so as to hasten its evaporation.

